    proclaim: "The [bold cyan]Forensic Integrity Ledger[/] is manifest."
    proclaim: "Cryptographic Seal: [bold magenta]HMAC-SHA256[/]"
    proclaim: "LIF-Multiplier: [bold green]INFINITY (Non-Repudiation Guaranteed)[/]"